# pydelphi disttibution build
#### Update the version tag to current date
poetry run bump-version

#### Build source distribution of pydelphi
poetry build -f sdist


#### Install the source distribution
##### untar the pydelphi-source-distribution
##### change directory to pydelphi-source-distribution
pip install -e .


